{"tid":1618721,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"下午三點，各位準備起義！","createTime":"2019-10-04T06:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T06:35:27.000Z","uid":45486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f6df694c50b025635e35cd19e6026d3c5979eb08","tid":1618721,"uid":45486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0284038ac0138d4ebf62f6973747994c9f3d090d","tid":1618721,"uid":48682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:25:12.000Z","msg":"出左去啦，仲等3點"},{"pid":"824255a87f9fbe06a7db2f7895e37a0eaabb7c2e","tid":1618721,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:28:17.000Z","msg":"全港武裝起義"},{"pid":"51564ce7fc59426d02391e75b094399a9010dcfa","tid":1618721,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:28:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">破解緊急法！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">只有全民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無&middot;限&middot;期</span>罷工罷課先可以救自己、救香港！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">早前政府宣布，香港各區發生暴動！今日宣布立緊急法</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">亦即係話，當日只要出過街嘅非警察人士，都有機會告你參與暴動</span>！<span style=\"color: red;\">要去狗屋坐48個鐘，而且定罪嘅話一坐就幾年</span>！<br />\n<br />\n打工反學嘅你，為你自己將來，呼籲大家，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡快組織無限期罷工、罷課</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有咁，先可以癱瘓社會運作，直到政府宣布徹底妥協為止！</span>"},{"pid":"41bafccfd26b20b2445a8533d81df5937337daad","tid":1618721,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:35:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">破解緊急法！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">只有全民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無&middot;限&middot;期</span>罷工罷課先可以救自己、救香港！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">早前政府宣布，香港各區發生暴動！今日宣布立緊急法</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">亦即係話，當日只要出過街嘅非警察人士，都有機會告你參與暴動</span>！<span style=\"color: red;\">要去狗屋坐48個鐘，而且定罪嘅話一坐就幾年</span>！<br />\n<br />\n打工反學嘅你，為你自己將來，呼籲大家，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡快組織無限期罷工、罷課</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有咁，先可以癱瘓社會運作，直到政府宣布徹底妥協為止！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n罷工，你可能面對被炒魷魚嘅風險，但罷工不需要附上刑責！警察唔可能上門捉你返工！<span style=\"color: red;\">只要齊心，換來嘅係政府徹底讓步！大家包括今日有出街嘅人亦唔會被告暴動！警察亦可以立即停止暴力，義士亦可以沉冤得雪</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如果大家唔齊心罷工，有一日警察會上門捉你，告你暴動！就算唔係，警察以後亦會變本加厲，用更重手對付大家！以後大家無機會出聲！</span>今日見到已經開槍謀殺義士！我地一定要立即制止納粹警暴歪風！請大家立即籌備無限期罷工、罷課！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>請文宣幫手將以上論點製作poster廣傳，多謝各位</strong>"}]}